Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.matrix

Class MatrixNode

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.matrix.MatrixNode
public class MatrixNode extends Object

Title: MatrixNode

Description:

Helper class which creates the individual nodes in the matrix. Note that we have up, down, left, and right attributes which denotes the elements near the given node. This is helpful for quick traversals/deletions.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
